text: Alina Sanko (born 31 December 1998; ) is a Russian model and beauty pageant who was crowned Miss Russia 2019. She represented Russia at the Miss World 2019 competition in London and reached the Top 12. ==Early life and education== Sanko was born in Azov. She graduates from Moscow State University of Land Management. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Russian models
